id: pm-42tb
title: Make list --ids repeatable for focused agent working-set refresh
description: "Allow list-family commands to accept repeated --ids flags as the same focused item-set filter as comma-separated --ids. This improves token-efficient agent refresh loops by avoiding repeated pm get calls or broad list scans. Duplicate check: searched list ids repeatable working set refresh; no open matching item found."
type: Task
status: closed
priority: 2
tags: []
created_at: "2026-06-06T19:14:09.143Z"
updated_at: "2026-06-06T19:39:58.281Z"
author: codex-sdk-continuation
parent: pm-mpbb
resolution: Delivered repeatable list --ids support for focused agent working-set refresh.
expected_result: Agents can pass repeated --ids flags to list commands and receive the same focused set as comma-separated ids.
actual_result: Bootstrap list filtering now merges repeated --ids; command help/docs/tests/manual smoke verify list-open returns exactly the requested item set.
